nk\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi//hk/legis/ord/427/s4.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪即係冇得告"},{"pid":"442a58988930b5a7a6c7bcc593b69a390cdda1de","tid":1495371,"uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇"},{"pid":"694cc730b48ea88056c1259a58db93f7684582f4","tid":1495371,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:58:57.000Z","msg":"問鄭若嬅<br />\n佢話告咪得"},{"pid":"2e92366a745687745befc16884eec35e44c86f8d","tid":1495371,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"無，香港刑事檢控權係律政司到"},{"pid":"07b184f6cf891f909401ab9ffd81b3cc4939a8ad","tid":1495371,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"996a657a21fd1ba90cbaae114ee71881f712b8c2","tid":1495371,"uid":242846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"睇律政頭...佢唔告都吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d44283ff35e36cb4c526d46987e7331e6959d2","tid":1495371,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"由律政司決定告邊條"},{"pid":"ab21ba5e80985fdee795f4f1108fc9c2a5885ecd","tid":1495371,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1972e7f4d65c70bff8286fc00d48ae30801a34f9","tid":1495371,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"呢個制度好有問題<br />\n太不公平<br />\n示威者就告到最重個條罪<br />\n你黑警同廢佬就同最輕微的罪去告"},{"pid":"0e9db821053a2186cc4164d4187dc299170a1a71","tid":1495371,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot